  <!-- EN: 【Second-rate】melee, attack the enemy will have a Armor Break effect.\n\nA blade made of iron used by the ancient cultivators is still very sharp, though it has been used for unknown years. -->
  <RI_Weapon_AncientBlade.description>【二品】近战兵器\n\n古修者使用的一种玄铁打造的弯刀，虽历经不知多少年，但依然十分锋利。</RI_Weapon_AncientBlade.description>
