  <!-- EN: Ancient rifle【Second-rate】 -->
  <RI_Weapon_AncientGun.label>玄铁灵铳【二品】</RI_Weapon_AncientGun.label>
  <!-- EN: 【Second-rate】Range weapon\n\nA fire-blaster shaped like a dragon head with a laser firing system. The weapon was said to be a blunderbuss, but its caliber was closer to a cannonball, and it fired hot pellets that were terrifying to kill. At the same time, the weapon can adjust the muzzle to shoot a high-temperature laser through the energy array. -->
  <RI_Weapon_AncientGun.description>【二品】远程兵器\n\n从古修的技术中，研究出的一种玄铁铳，可以释放大威力的灵气子弹。这种灵铳在多人列装时，会互相感应，产生连携效果。</RI_Weapon_AncientGun.description>
