  <!-- EN: Ancient power fist【Second-rate】 -->
  <RI_Weapon_AncientPowerBoxing.label>古修动力铁拳【二品】</RI_Weapon_AncientPowerBoxing.label>
  <!-- EN: 【Second-rate】melee, attack the enemy will have a Vertigo effect.\n\nA pair of push-dagger with a faint Qi. A kind of push-dagger weapon made by thrumbo horn. Small and chic, but the attack speed is very fast, contains a powerful lethality. -->
  <RI_Weapon_AncientPowerBoxing.description>【二品】近战兵器\n\n古修者使用的一种古代拳套，内部含有动力组件，可以爆发出更大的冲击力。</RI_Weapon_AncientPowerBoxing.description>
